{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Offer 0% Emergency Loans to Stranded Citizens for flights and accommodation",
        "additional_details": "British citizens have been left stranded abroad due to COVID-19. Flights have been cancelled and refunds have not been issued. Commercial airlines have continued to flaunt flights to desperate customers, knowing full well that they will not go ahead due to travel restrictions. People have spent thousands in an effort to get home, which have left them without money to pay for flights home/ accommodation. Some are in need of life saving medication for their conditions which they can not afford.",
        "background": "British citizens are currently stranded abroad with no money to pay for flights home, food or accommodation. Due to the current situation, hostels and hotels have closed, and repatriation flights are far and beyond what is affordable for 80% of people.",
